reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars HOOBRO End Table with Charging Station - Smart and Stylish Convenience!
reviews.reviewText: The HOOBRO End Table with Charging Station is a brilliant fusion of modern convenience and timeless design. This smart end table has not only elevated the functionality of my living space but has also become an integral part of my daily routine.First and foremost, the built-in charging station with USB ports is an absolute game-changer. The ability to charge my devices directly from the end table eliminates the need for extra adapters and cords cluttering my space. The USB ports are conveniently placed, allowing me to keep my smartphone, tablet, or other gadgets powered up and within arm's reach.The design of the end table is both sleek and practical. The classic color and clean lines make it a versatile addition to any room, seamlessly blending with various decor styles. The compact size is perfect for smaller spaces, and the smooth finish adds a touch of sophistication.Assembly was a breeze, with easy-to-follow instructions and all necessary hardware included. The sturdy construction of the end table became evident as I assembled it, providing confidence in its durability.The spacious tabletop and lower shelf offer ample storage for everyday items, such as books, a lamp, or decorative accents. The added convenience of having a dedicated space for essentials enhances the overall organization and tidiness of my living space.The durability of the HOOBRO End Table is impressive. The high-quality materials used in its construction ensure that it stands up well to daily use, providing both reliability and longevity.Whether you're a tech-savvy individual or someone looking to streamline their living space, the HOOBRO End Table with Charging Station is a practical and stylish solution. Its combination of smart features, elegant design, and affordable price point make it a five-star addition to any home. Highly recommended!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice but a bit small
reviews.reviewText: My son like this table. It goes well with the platform bed he got recently. The outlets are very handy for him. I just wish it were a little bit bigger. Just check the dimensions if size may be an issue for you or your space.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Amazing: Small Yet Very Sturdy
reviews.reviewText: I needed a small, sturdy table for my printer with shelves for paper and ink, etc. Having USB and electrical outlets is a huge plus. This end table fits my needs perfectly and is very sturdy with adjustable feet for leveling, if needed. Great value: I highly recommend it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice little end table.
reviews.reviewText: I think this is the first ever piece of furniture that I assembled without stripping at least one screw. Everything lined up and assembly was super easy. The 120v and USB plugs on the front add extra convenience. Packaging was good with all the important pieces protected by Styrofoam. Be aware it's small, but if that's what you are looking for, it's perfect.
These are adorable little tables. A little small but great for my small space.Easy to put together
Cute and easy to assemble; a bit small, but cute
Bought these for my spare bedroom and easy to put together. Love the USB and power outlets built in. Good quality for the price

Unless the furniture in the photos are also small, this table is tiny. I'm 5'4" and it's around knee height. The surface area is about the size of a standard sheet of paper. I will be putting a coffee maker on this which is heavier than the table itself so I am concerned for it's stability. Good thing it has tiers so I can put weight on the bottom. The photos have it around the height of a chair's armrest so it's a good 20cm lower than I was expecting... I really should have measured and not trusted marketing photos
I have only had for a day but it seems like it is a decent tabel. And put it together without any issues. It is very user friendly with putting it together. The plugs work well and it looks nice.
